OL,3,CFormer restaurateur handed 15-year
OL,4,Cprison sentence for sex offences
OL,6,FA former Jersey restaurateur has been
OL,7,Fsentenced to 15 years in prison for a
OL,8,Fseries of sexual offences - including
OL,9,Frape - at Jersey's Royal Court.
OL,11,FGavin Neil Roberts, 44, appeared for
OL,12,Fsentencing at the Royal Court on
OL,13,FFriday 8 November 2024.
OL,15,FAfter an eight-day trial in February,
OL,16,FRoberts was found guilty of rape, two
OL,17,Ffurther sexual offences, and three
OL,18,Fassault charges against two women.
