OL,3,CFormer restaurateur handed 15-year
OL,4,Cprison sentence for sex offences
OL,6,FHe previously denied all those charges
OL,7,Fbut pleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,8,Fgrave and criminal assault against one
OL,9,Fof the women.
OL,11,FThe extensive prison sentence hopes to
OL,12,Fset a precedence for future cases
OL,13,Frelated to serious sex offences.
OL,15,FRoberts' first complainant presented
OL,16,Fevidence that on 2 October 2022, in
OL,17,FBath Street, Gavin Roberts assaulted
OL,18,Fher by pushing her against a doorway
OL,19,Fand grabbing her by the neck.
