OL,6,FRoberts was also found guilty of
OL,7,Fraping the complainant and using an
OL,8,Fobject for penetration, all without
OL,9,Fconsent and without reasonable belief
OL,10,Fthat consent had been given, while
OL,11,Fabroad on 15 October 2022.
OL,13,FAdditionally, Roberts pleaded guilty
OL,14,Fto two counts of Grave and Criminal
OL,15,FAssault on the same complainant that
OL,16,Foccurred between 27 and 30 October
OL,17,F2022, in St Helier, resulting in
OL,18,Fsignificant facial injuries and body
OL,19,Fbruising.
