OL,6,FThe second complainant detailed
OL,7,Fassaults between 28 February 2022 and
OL,8,F1 September 2022, in St Saviour, where
OL,9,FRoberts attacked her by laying on top
OL,10,Fof her and placing his hands around
OL,11,Fher neck. She was able to escape and
OL,12,Fsecure herself.
OL,14,FHowever, Roberts again assaulted the
OL,15,Fsecond complainant three days later by
OL,16,Fgrabbing her neck and pushing her
OL,17,Fagainst a wall.
